platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: When a much-loved Canadian icon launches an innovative way for us Canucks to get our Timmys faster and easier, well, its a natural Editors Choice. We love that the apps simple, scrollable menu makes it easy to preorder exactly what we want. The app offers up the closest participating pick-up locations, complete with map and directions. And we can use Apple Pay, an easy way to top up our Tims card account. The best part: skipping the line and heading straight for the Mobile Pickup signs!
